ibiting an approach to equilibrium in physically reasonable\ntimes. The initial conditions chosen by Fermi, Pasta and Ulam were not generic\nand below threshold and would have required possibly an infinite time to reach\nequilibrium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 1996 16:16:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 1997 10:41:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 1998 14:53:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-28"}
